Detailed Description

Map implementations.

Any implementation of the map in CDS library is derived from class map_tag. It means that 

                boost::type_traits::is_base_of< cds::map::map_tag, L>::value

is true iff L is an implementation of the map.

The common interface of the map implementation see Map common interface.
